windows:
website GIT, choose windows and the install will be loading.
install
select lauch git bash
open git bash

##confirm:
git --version 

##initial configurations, name of username

git config --global user.name "Your name"

##configure the email address: that's important been the same of github to not make conflicts, so 

git config --global user.email youremail@email.com 

##check the list of configurations

git config --list

done. 
